content:
Set Initial Selections and Global Filters in the Dashboard

Set initial selections and global filters that appear when the dashboard first opens. The viewer can change them while viewing the dashboard.

Set Initial Selections in the Dashboard
If the dashboard contains selection-based widgets, set initial selections applied when the dashboard first opens. For example, select a bar in a bar chart and set it as the initial selection.

Set Initial Global Filters in the Dashboard
If the dashboard contains global filters, set the initial filters that are applied when the dashboard first opens. The viewer can change them while viewing the dashboard.

Global filters apply to all queries unless configured otherwise.
title: Setting Initial Selections and Global Filters in Salesforce Dashboards
